title: Spyder Auto Install: Altezza & Euro-Tail Style Tail Lights Overview (Honda Accord)
description:
This video offers a general overview of how to install a set of Spyder Auto Altezza-type tail lights, which should give you a good idea of how to install your set.

This video demonstrates how to install a set of euro-style or "Altezza" tail lights on a Honda Accord.
